88
00:06:19,727 --> 00:06:21,527
Apa?

89
00:06:21,527 --> 00:06:23,027
Ternyata kamar mandi.

90
00:06:23,027 --> 00:06:25,227
Benar.

91
00:06:25,227 --> 00:06:29,227
Tapi di sini ada panah.

92
00:06:29,227 --> 00:06:33,627
Masalahnya ia menunjuk ke arah bak.

93
00:06:33,627 --> 00:06:37,427
Bukan bak, tapi pancaran.

94
00:06:37,427 --> 00:06:41,127
Ada catatan di depan panah di wastafel.

95
00:06:42,127 --> 00:06:45,827
"Burungnya dirawat, ya!"

96
00:06:47,427 --> 00:06:49,027
Burung apa?

97
00:06:49,027 --> 00:06:51,327
Apa maksudnya boneka ini?

98
00:06:51,327 --> 00:06:53,927
Sepertinya dia punya paruh.

99
00:06:53,927 --> 00:06:57,627
Tapi bagaimana cara kita merawatnya?

100
00:06:57,627 --> 00:06:59,827
Boneka yang aneh.

101
00:06:59,827 --> 00:07:02,027
Aku tidak tahu.

102
00:07:02,027 --> 00:07:06,727
Rasanya aku pernah lihat boneka seperti ini sebelumnya.

103
00:07:06,727 --> 00:07:08,127
Karena kita sudah buntu...

104
00:07:08,127 --> 00:07:09,127
Artinya...

105
00:07:09,127 --> 00:07:11,927
-Kita harus bertanya. -Apa?

106
00:07:11,927 --> 00:07:13,827
Tanya ke Conan!

107
00:07:16,527 --> 00:07:18,027
Tidak boleh?

108
00:07:18,027 --> 00:07:19,627
Kenapa tidak?

109
00:07:19,627 --> 00:07:22,127
Aku yakin dia tahu jawabannya.

110
00:07:23,727 --> 00:07:26,227
Conan sudah tidak sakit, bukan?

111
00:07:26,227 --> 00:07:28,527
Ayo kita hubungi dia.

112
00:07:28,527 --> 00:07:32,127
Kita harus mencari Maria secepat mungkin, bukan?

113
00:07:37,327 --> 00:07:41,327
Aku benci meminta bantuan sama si tukang ingkar janji itu,

114
00:07:41,327 --> 00:07:43,427
tapi kami tidak punya pilihan.

115
00:07:45,827 --> 00:07:47,427
Aku tahu!

116
00:07:47,427 --> 00:07:50,827
Shinichi Kudo punya saudara kembar

117
00:07:50,827 --> 00:07:53,227
dan saudaranya itu yang mati.

118
00:07:53,227 --> 00:07:56,727
Bagaimana kalau kita sebarkan khabar angin itu ke internet?

119
00:07:56,727 --> 00:07:59,527
Orang-orang pasti segera tahu kalau itu bohong!

120
00:07:59,527 --> 00:08:01,827
Apa kau tidak paham, Shinichi?

121
00:08:01,827 --> 00:08:06,227
Kalau Organisasi Hitam tahu kau masih hidup...

122
00:08:06,227 --> 00:08:09,627
Ya, aku tahu.

123
